\chapter*{Preface}
\thispagestyle{empty} 
HiFrost is nuclear polarized target apparatus consisting of a dilution refrigerator, internal ``holding'' magnetic coil, microwave guide and NMR coil.  External components of HiFrost include a polarizing magnet, microwave generating EIO, pump and vacuum system to run the dilution refrigerator, and the Q-Meter/Yale Card set up for running the NMR. 
